FBIS4-58689 "drnes088_j_94025" FBIS-NES-94-088 Daily Report 6 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Fighting Continues; Airport Bombed; Calls for Peace Made Fighting Continues; Airport Bombed; Calls for Peace Made Northern Plane Shot Down During Airport Attack NC0605123794 Paris AFP in English 1228 GMT 6 May 94 NC0605123794 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Aden, Yemen, May 6 (AFP) -- A warplane was shot down as it attacked Aden Airport on Friday, officials said here. The plane, from forces loyal to President 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, a northerner, launched the raid as a French ship was evacuating foreigners from this southern port.
